The '''Vehicle Maintenance Energizer''' was a device used to maintain starships and vehicles. It also provided ships with energy. The [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] used such devices on [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]].

==Behind the scenes==
This device still goes by the name given to it by [[Kenner Products|Kenner]] when they released it as an accessory in their Vintage line in [[1982]]. It came with 8 [[Hydrospanner/Legends|Hydrospanners]] and 2 energy hoses. On the box, [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] was seen using the device.

